name: EAU DE PARFUM SPRAY
description: The PERFECT INTENSE MARC JACOBS design is a chic reinterpretation of the original perfect bottle. Crafted in collaboration with Marc Jacobs himself and featuring an elegant blend of unexpected elements, the weighted glass base is inspired by the femininity and grace of a classic parfum.

name: MISS DIOR EAU DE
description: Miss Dior Eau de Parfum reinvents itself with a new scent.In 1947, Miss Dior was born out of a wild impetus where the pressing desire to re-enchant the lives of women and open up their eyes, once again, to the sparkling colors of love was felt.

name: Maison Francis Kurkdjian
description: Luminous and sophisticated, Baccarat Rouge 540 lays on the skin like an amber, floral and woody breeze. A poetic alchemy. A graphic and highly condensed signature. Paraben free. Made in France.

name: Boyfriend Eau de Parfum
description: Boyfriend is sweet, spicy, woodsy and warm. With top notes of dark plum and myrrh blended together to forge a smell that is irresistible and captivating. Middle notes of night blooming jasmine and benzoin tears creates a musky spicy, vanilla sweet fragrance.

name: CHANCE EAU TENDRE
description: A green and fruity grapefruit-quince accord intertwines with the softness of jasmine and the smoothness of white musks for an intoxicatingly light, floral trail.

name: Wisam Asgharali Eau de Parfum
description: Perfume Wisam Eau de Parfum by Asgharali is oriental men's perfume with musk, amber and floral notes.Fresh and fruity, the fragrance begins in the top note with pineapple and citrus notes.

name: J'ADORE
description: An iconic fragrance, J’adore Eau de Parfum is the grand feminine floral by the House of Dior.Finely crafted down to the last detail, like a custom-made flower, J'adore is a bouquet of the most beautiful flowers from around the world.

name: Pink Peppercorns, Ground
description: A straight-A cheerleader who smells of strawberries and can eat ghost chiles raw to prove she’s tougher than you.

name: Gucci Bloom Eau de Parfum
description: Gucci Bloom is a classic floral fragrance that you’ll opt for again and again. It features notes of rangoon creeper, jasmine bud and tuberose for a scent meant to embody the Gucci woman.

name: Maison Francis Kurkdjian Baccarat Rouge
description: Fine fragrances containing a high dose of natural ingredients can be subject to slight variations. In the same way wines vary from year to year, so can perfume.

name: EAUX DE PARFUM
description: A bit of a leper in the spice world – always begging to be used and used so rarely. A shame considering these have significantly more flavor than their pale counterparts.

name: My Way Eau de Parfum
description: An elegant, floral fragrance for women that invites you to broaden your horizons and live meaningful encounters around the world.
